SPLIT QUERIES:
==============

After extracting second run queries, it can be divided into parts to run in parallel in condor system.
This script divides the given query file into valid XML sub parts that can be used for individual condor runs.

USAGE:
python split_queries.py <input_query_file.xml> <output_file_prefix> <num_of_queries_per_file>

This is common for KBP 2013 and 2014 query files.